    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Overview</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Misa</i> is a sorceress finding her way in a colorful  fantasy world sprinkled with french expressions. To fight your way through, you will build spells by combining multiples effects and items to increase their power. Make a good use of all your resources to end up victorious ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/b9f597d9e516dfb6cc7025ca823b22cd.poster.avif?t=1737574718\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/b9f597d9e516dfb6cc7025ca823b22cd.webm?t=1737574718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/b9f597d9e516dfb6cc7025ca823b22cd.mp4?t=1737574718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><br>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Travel through 3 biomes</strong> each with its boss and monsters that have unique abilities.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/6eee8969e8f347338a045e2f2da87e2f.poster.avif?t=1737574718\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/6eee8969e8f347338a045e2f2da87e2f.webm?t=1737574718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/6eee8969e8f347338a045e2f2da87e2f.mp4?t=1737574718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create your own spells</strong> and build using looted items :<br>    50+ effects to stack buffs and debuffs onto your targets<br>    30+ cores to determine your spells actions &amp; spells bonuses<br>    30+ relics that grants you a passive bonus for the whole run</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/3804033b620605cc16a4180849cb6f2e.poster.avif?t=1737574718\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/3804033b620605cc16a4180849cb6f2e.webm?t=1737574718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/3804033b620605cc16a4180849cb6f2e.mp4?t=1737574718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each destination is a resource</strong> in itself, so optimize your path to use them wisely. Will you risk starting by the dungeon to get new cores or use one of the few shops to upgrade your spells first ?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/b5ad2a4e6fa01e1ae80b5996ef1a4c59.poster.avif?t=1737574718\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/b5ad2a4e6fa01e1ae80b5996ef1a4c59.webm?t=1737574718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/b5ad2a4e6fa01e1ae80b5996ef1a4c59.mp4?t=1737574718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strengthen your build</strong> by using all the potential of the spell smithing village. You can always count on good allies (If you can pay the cost).</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/ad2f46a9423158bfc07107e74f5b5ce1.poster.avif?t=1737574718\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/ad2f46a9423158bfc07107e74f5b5ce1.webm?t=1737574718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277840/extras/ad2f46a9423158bfc07107e74f5b5ce1.mp4?t=1737574718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>... And more to discover ... !</i></p>",
